## Row Context
### measuring each row, not used in measures only used in calculated columns
if([Age]>=18, "Can Vote", "Can't vote")


## Calculate Function
Chennai Sales= calculate( Sum([Sales]), location= "Chennai")
All loc Sales= calculate( Sum([Sales]), all(location))
